1. Copy config_example.php to config.php
2. Modify config.php based on your account information.  This will include
   at least the api key, shared secret and account name.  All of these should
   be available via gliffy.com

   You can test this using the script test_configuration.php  It contains comments in the script
   to tell you how to use it.

3. Copy all files to somewhere in your PHP include path
4. In your application, do

   require "Gliffy.php"

   It will require the other necessary files.
5. Refer to /examples/ for helpful examples to get you started.

